    <body id="registration">
      <div id="backButton">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Back</a>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
            <% if(error && error.length > 0) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                    <%= error %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            <% if(success && success.length > 0) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
                    <%= success %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
		<div id="mainbox" style="text-align:center">
		<div id="introbox">
		<h2> The Freecycle Distribution Project</h2>
		<br><br>
		<h5 style="line-height:30px;font-size:19px;color:white;text-shadow: 0px 0px 10px black;text-align:left">
		&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbspWeâ€™ll be creating a time exchange in which people either offer up their own services in exchange for some number of hours or request services from others for some number of hours. 
		The number of hours each person has will be displayed on their own page, as well as their contact information, so that others can check that they actually have enough hours to pay for the services. 
		<br><br>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbspBoth parties - the service requester and the service provider - initially agree to a set number of hours in exchange for a service. 
		The hours is then held separately / frozen. After a service is completed, the frozen hours will be released to the service provider. 
		The frozen hours can also be released in parts after the completion of each part of the service. </h5>
		</div>
      <div id="signupBox" style="display:block;float:left;margin-left: 200px;">
	<h2> Register </h2>
	<hr>
        <form action="/register" method="POST">
	<input type="text" placeholder="First Name" name="firstName" required>
	<input type="text" placeholder="Last Name" name="lastName" required>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Username" name="username" required>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Email" name="email" required>
        <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" required><br>
        <button type="submit">Sign Up</button>
        </form>
      </div>
	  <div>
    </body>
</html>
